Can you bully-proof a workout studio? How does that work?&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;
Counsellors Maathavan and Randee from the Bully-Free team recently dropped by @f45_training_jurongcbd to share tips with the trainers on how to identify bullying behaviour and how they can prevent and manage such behaviours.&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;
This is an inaugural partnership as @f45_training_jurongcbd is looking at expanding its range of classes with F45 Prodigy, a class that is specifically for youth aged 11 to 17. It was a very engaging and fruitful sharing session, and the Bully-Free team looks forward to more community collaborations in the future!&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;
ICYMI: To raise awareness on bullying,&nbsp;Singapore Children‚Äôs Society has collaborated with the National Heritage Board to present Scribble Town, an interactive exhibition for children aged 9 to 12. The exhibition is held at the Sun Yat Sen Nanyang Memorial Hall from NOW till 31 January&nbsp;2021.&nbsp;See you there!

#f45 #f45training #antibullying #SayNotoBullying #schoolholidayactivity #exhibition #museum #ilovemuseums #sgchildrensociety

