Let‚Äôs hear from the author, Mr Goh Eck Kheng, on the book creation process as he shares how he navigates a difficult topic like sexual abuse prevention to make it accessible for children to understand in a warm and reassuring way. Picture books enable children to approach difficult subjects in an age-appropriate manner and illustrations can help to fill in the subtext when words are not enough to convey.

