Have you ever wondered who is behind that reassuring voice when a child calls Tinkle Friend? Read on to find out more: www.childrensociety.org.sg/centre-updates/you-have-got-a-friend-in-tinkle-friend
&nbsp;
Tinkle Friend is a national toll-free helpline and online chatline for all primary-school-aged children in Singapore that provides support, advice, and information to lonely and distressed children, especially in situations when their parents or main caregivers are unavailable. For more information, please visit&nbsp;www.tinklefriend.sg

